{"TopicId":197592,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Forum UI Changes","CreatedByName":"Clamp-o-Tron","CreatedById":201818,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T20:53:21Z","PageNum":9,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-22T17:04:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871244\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603384060\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n35 minutes ago, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it possible to return those buttons to where they belong, or is that just part of the forum software update?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s on the list of Things We\u0027d Like Done\u003Csup\u003ETM\u003C/sup\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-22T20:05:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d say, well-done.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022legende-cuisson-boeuf-en.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.25\u0022 height=\u0022450\u0022 width=\u0022800\u0022 src=\u0022https://buythermopro.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/legende-cuisson-boeuf-en.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Entropian","CreatedById":205453,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-22T22:20:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks IT for the less whitespace change!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-22T22:32:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871072\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603357336\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269272\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022steve_v\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, steve_v said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt might be wise to hold off on using or creating stylesheet overrides until they\u0027ve finished buggering about with it, things are bound to break randomly until it settles down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah... I dont know about Hebarusan, or others, but I\u0027ll be holding off on updating/tweaking my dark forum theme till after the dust settles and ManeIT finishes up.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd yeah, if anyone was already using my dark theme, yes... it broke with this latest forum update \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603352654\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269272\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022steve_v\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 hours ago, steve_v said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEd, here\u0027s what the frontpage looks like for me, with uBlock applied to the most useless elements (banner, sidebar, link to modhost nobody uses, etc, etc.):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://damnation.dynu.net/nextcloud/index.php/s/FndpzYsiiE6qmpB/preview\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022preview\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002246.63\u0022 height=\u0022560\u0022 style=\u0022width:800px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://damnation.dynu.net/nextcloud/index.php/s/FndpzYsiiE6qmpB/preview\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSee how much cleaner that is with just a few clicks? See how only forum related things remain?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMinimal sidebar whitespace?...\u003Cbr\u003E\nLike this? \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022JUF7Kju.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002291.25\u0022 height=\u0022679\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/JUF7Kju.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nand below is the front page before the recent forum changes. With all but the basic stuff *I* would ever be using:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/eLpXv\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/a/eLpXv\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-22T22:51:00Z\u0022 title=\u002210/22/2020 10:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 22, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Stone Blue\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-22T22:47:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871204\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603380991\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156657\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HebaruSan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, HebaruSan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, my Stylish override\u00A0removes the sidebar because I don\u0027t find anything in there useful (it\u0027s even worse on the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/discover/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EAll Activity\u003C/a\u003E screen, where it\u0027s just a Newsletter announcement that I\u0027ll never sign up for in exchange for making every post 40% narrower). If you want it back, this is the line to remove:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-css prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E#\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EipsLayout_sidebar\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan class=\u0022pun\u0022\u003E,\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup... My Stylish theme does away with it also, for the same reasons\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-22T23:03:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871385\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603405932\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah... I dont know about Hebarusan, or others, but I\u0027ll be holding off on updating/tweaking my dark forum theme till after the dust settles and ManeIT finishes up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI expect the near-term changes to be aesthetic rather than structural (compared to the recent upgrade itself), but if something does break, it probably won\u0027t be that hard to fix it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnybody else notice there\u0027s a Preview button now?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022dtGS3ND.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002245.88\u0022 height=\u0022178\u0022 width=\u0022388\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/dtGS3ND.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-22T23:18:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871395\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603407792\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022156657\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HebaruSan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, HebaruSan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnybody else notice there\u0027s a Preview button now?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/dtGS3ND.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022dtGS3ND.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002245.88\u0022 height=\u0022178\u0022 width=\u0022388\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/dtGS3ND.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalwayshasbeen.meme\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor real, though, the preview was added shortly after (or concurrently) with the transition to Invision. IIRC, there were reports that WYSINWYG, so that option was enabled.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steve_v","CreatedById":69272,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-22T23:47:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871385\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603405932\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExactly like that \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EPersonally I\u0027m not looking for a \u0022night mode\u0022 theme (light is fine, just not actinic), so I\u0027ll probably tweak the colours a little.\u003Cbr\u003E\nAside, is there an alternative to userstyles.org that works with stylus and isn\u0027t unusably slow? I know you put your stuff on github like a sensible person, but others do not... poke poke\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156657-hebarusan/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022156657\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156657-hebarusan/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HebaruSan\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T00:27:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871406\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603410448\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269272\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022steve_v\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n40 minutes ago, steve_v said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EPersonally I\u0027m not looking for a \u0022night mode\u0022 theme (light is fine, just not actinic), so I\u0027ll probably tweak the colours a little.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease! Feel free to completely use mine as a base to tweak to your liking. I totally ripped this off from nbz\u0027s lighter blue theme. THEY did all the code... All I did (with permission), was to tweak the colors mainly, and did some minor moving around and hiding of stuff *I* didnt need. Loo at nbz\u0027s... theirs might be a better starting point for the colors you want... vOv\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u0027m all for a lot moar peeps to offer up alternatives to just the 3 or 4 styles that have been on Userstyles for years... (not counting the one Hebarusan just added \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E )... the moar choices, the merrier.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nMatter of fact, heres my Github repo. I have some older versions where I added moar tweaks:\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/StoneBlue/KSP-Forum-Dark-Theme\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/StoneBlue/KSP-Forum-Dark-Theme\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPretty open license, as stated at the bottom of the README \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-23T00:29:15Z\u0022 title=\u002210/23/2020 12:29  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 23, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Stone Blue\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RandomKerbal","CreatedById":206026,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T03:54:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps\u00A0the tittle wordings can be larger... \u0022[Minimum KSP version - 1.8]\u00A0\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Ev1.7\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/gZsQDG7/scrnli-10-21-2020-9-20-26-PM.png\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022scrnli-10-21-2020-9-20-26-PM\u0022 data-ratio=\u002275.25\u0022 style=\u0022border-style:none;vertical-align:middle;\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.ibb.co/gZsQDG7/scrnli-10-21-2020-9-20-26-PM.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steve_v","CreatedById":69272,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T04:33:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871419\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603412835\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLoo at nbz\u0027s... theirs might be a better starting point\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I do prefer nbz\u0027s colour choice, but I gave up after about 20 minutes of constant 504s and infinite spinners on userstyles.org.\u003Cbr\u003E\nI can\u0027t tweak what I can\u0027t obtain, which is why I went with yours, as it\u0027s served in a sensible manner as a flat file on github. Userstyles is a hellhole these days even on the rare occasions when it does work, stylish has gone proprietary and shoves an android app in your face at every turn, etc. etc.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nIf you do happen to have a copy of nbz\u0027s theme, do you recon you could mirror it somewhere so I can have a play with it? Of course I can\u0027t see the licence on the thing I can\u0027t obtain either...\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871469\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603425261\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022206026\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RandomKerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n40 minutes ago, RandomKerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps\u00A0the tittle wordings can be larger...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat \u003Cem\u003Eis\u003C/em\u003E sarcasm, right? It\u0027s huge already.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T10:43:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a counter-procrastination layout. To do the work instead of chatting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RandomKerbal","CreatedById":206026,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T11:28:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871473\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603427609\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269272\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022steve_v\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, steve_v said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat \u003Cem\u003Eis\u003C/em\u003E sarcasm, right? It\u0027s huge already.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut not as enormous as the old one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steve_v","CreatedById":69272,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T13:29:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871545\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603452530\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022206026\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RandomKerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, RandomKerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut not as enormous as the old one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps. Frankly I find this current trend for enormous buttons, enormous fonts, enormous blank areas, completely unnecessary boxes/borders/padding, social-media links/likes/rep/ratings, and information-free icons, animations, and\u00A0 other random graphical elements properly perplexing.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe purpose of a forum is primarily discussion, and secondarily a repository of information. As such, the more discussion and information one can get on a page and still be navigable the better. Bonus points for minimising bandwidth hogging graphics and CPU/memory hogging javascript, particularly if you intend people to use the site on mobile devices. Not everyone has this years super-phone and/or a high bandwidth downlink you know.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nHuge titles do nothing for signal/noise ratio or information density. All they achieve is making me scroll down further to get to the content. If they\u0027re remote fonts, they slow down page loading as well.\u003Cbr\u003E\nWhat\u003Cem\u003E would\u003C/em\u003E be nice WRT the topic titles is eliminating some of that padding above them. Even with the huge font, there\u0027s still more screen devoted to blank space, buttons, ratings and follower counters than to content.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n---\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022preview\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002247.13\u0022 height=\u0022565\u0022 style=\u0022width:800px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://damnation.dynu.net/nextcloud/index.php/s/YdpLjmRgyHcBydc/preview\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd somewhere down here, pushed off the bottom of the image by all the silly bling, there be \u003Cs\u003Edragons\u003C/s\u003E content.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-23T14:05:34Z\u0022 title=\u002210/23/2020 02:05  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 23, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by steve_v\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T15:01:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSignature size restrictions are off btw\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerminator K-100","CreatedById":204357,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T15:06:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603465260\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152223\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Aperture Science\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, Aperture Science said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSignature size restrictions are off btw\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah but you don\u0027t have to make us suffer with your huge font size just to make a point\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T15:07:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871654\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603465582\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204357\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerminator1000\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n26 minutes ago, Kerminator1000 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah but you don\u0027t have to make us suffer with your huge font size just to make a point\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-23T15:33:37Z\u0022 title=\u002210/23/2020 03:33  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 23, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Guest\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerminator K-100","CreatedById":204357,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T15:09:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs that just your signature?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T15:14:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871658\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603465753\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204357\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerminator1000\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n57 minutes ago, Kerminator1000 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs that just your signature?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, just the usual. Why?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-23T16:07:11Z\u0022 title=\u002210/23/2020 04:07  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 23, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Guest\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steve_v","CreatedById":69272,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T15:29:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603465260\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152223\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Aperture Science\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n26 minutes ago, Aperture Science said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSignature size restrictions are off btw\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat broke rendering in the most hilarious of ways for a minute there. Top notch job.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nCareful with this stuff though, you\u0027re starting to give me ideas...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerminator K-100","CreatedById":204357,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T15:31:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223871678\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197592\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603466968\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269272\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022steve_v\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, steve_v said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCareful with this stuff though, you\u0027re starting to give me ideas...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh no\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"steve_v","CreatedById":69272,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T15:44:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup, a 50k by 50k jpeg bomb in your sig also breaks rendering. This is fun, what else can we break?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wonder what this does...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[snip]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAwww, someone put a limit on inline image dimensions. Boring.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-23T21:08:41Z\u0022 title=\u002210/23/2020 09:08  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 23, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Vanamonde\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"computercat04","CreatedById":207723,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T16:49:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe UI is looking strange again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T16:57:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet\u0027s not break the forums in this thread, ok? There\u0027s already a test thread for it, and it\u0027s pretty good.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EchoLima","CreatedById":61992,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-23T16:58:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne thing I do like is that the title is a separate element from the thread, and is visible on the top of every page. Helps if I\u0027m ever deep in a thread and forget what the topic is...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-23T16:58:51Z\u0022 title=\u002210/23/2020 04:58  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 23, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by EchoLima\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}